dct_description_sm: Text on verso: Geography of South America. Relief indicated by hachures. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1863 by A.J. Johnson in the Clerks Office of the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York." In upper right margin: 70. In lower right margin: 71. Probably issued in: Johnson's new illustrated (steel plate) family atlas ... New York : Johnson and Ward, 1863.
